miscarriage i'm sure this question has been asked a zillion times i'm sorry i had a miscarriage around weeks i bled for about days i stopped bleeding about days ago just yesterday i started feeling very emotional and crampy should i expect a period this soon or might i still be pregnant i'm kind of scared to take a pregnancy test probably more scared that it might be negative i just have no idea what to expect i haven't been to the doctor i saw no reason to go and if you're going to tell me to just go to the doctor don't bother answering thanks for all of the support through this crazy time first off i am so sorry for your loss i too had a m c at w and i bled for about a week my next period skipped and then the one after that was normal every woman's body is different tho i did have to have a d c performed one of my friends who had a m c also did not have to have a d c done so its just different but if you are having cramping i would suggest seeing the doctor you could be placing yourself in great danger of infection if you have had a m c and don't get checked out very early in pregnancy bleeding can occur it does not mean you have had a m c what makes you think you have you may be able to find a pregnancy test at your local dollar store if you dont want to spend the at the drugstore take that first and go from there i wish you the best Miscarriage Pregnancy Menstrual cycle Abortion Stomach cancer Non-Hodgkin's lymphoma Obstetrics Gonorrhoea Prostate cancer Urinary incontinence Childbirth Pregnancy test Coeliac disease Fertility awareness Stroke Endometrial cancer Cytomegalovirus Stillbirth Abortion debate HIV test Chemical abortion Premature birth Breastfeeding Oral contraceptive Gynecologic hemorrhage Twin Hormone replacement therapy (trans) Folic acid Milton H. Erickson Singlish Rei Ayanami EastEnders Spina bifida Polycystic ovary syndrome Turner syndrome Endometriosis Marilyn Monroe Diabetic retinopathy Traumatic brain injury Psoriasis Bleeding Pelvic inflammato